Name: pinyin-jyutping-sentence
Version: 0.9
Summary: Convert a Chinese sentence to Pinyin or Jyutping
Home-page: https://github.com/lucwastiaux/python-pinyin-jyutping-sentence
Author: Luc Wastiaux
